    Object:
    _____________

    The SOUCIS functor manages the signalisation of non fatal troubles.

    It returns the current value of the trouble.
    Followed by an integer N1, it sets the current trouble flag.

    Remarqs:
    ------

    The trouble is increasing but can be zeroed.

    Each assistant manages it's own souci.

